txt.en: Tomb-robbers have long sifted through the ruined paths of Ann√∫minas and the tombs of the fallen Kings of old. The Rangers of the North ally with any who would take up arms to keep these thieves and scoundrels at bay.
Desperation and cunning make the tomb-robbers who flock to Evendim dangerous, but they have proven no match for a stalwart hero such as yourself.
